<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[Hind.]</ety> <def>In Oriental countries, a
respectful form of address given to a woman; mother.</def> <au>Balfour
(Cyc. of India).</au>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

